cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.AI 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to restore color in underwater images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves 3D structure calculation, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). The use of a dataset and quantitative evaluation suggests cs.MM (Multimedia), while the use of stereo imaging suggests cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the use of parameter estimation and library evaluation suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
